OL,5, A greater number of people are         
OL,6, borrowing more and expecting to save   
OL,7, less as the rising cost of living bites
OL,8, in the UK, official figures suggest.   
OL,10,FNearly one in five (17%) said they were
OL,11,Fborrowing more than they did a year    
OL,12,Fago, based on a survey conducted in    
OL,13,FMarch.                                 
OL,15,FSome 43% said they would not be able to
OL,16,Fsave money in the next 12 months.      
OL,18,FAt no time in the past two years has   
OL,19,Fthat figure been any higher, the Office
OL,20,Ffor National Statistics (ONS) said.    
